# Polevoy, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Polevoy () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 3 as of 2010.
Geography
Polevoy is located 48&nbsp;km southwest of Kabansk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Baykalsky Priboy is the nearest rural locality.
